RequestBody: Select asset_id from (select distinct ah.asset_id, count(distinct ah.asset_history_id) as Rec_countfrom asset_history ah join asset_history_attributes ahaon ah.asset_history_id = aha.asset_history_idgroup by ah.asset_id) tmp where rec_count > 5

Select * from (select ah.asset_id, ah.asset_history_id, ah.type as assetHistoryType, ah.asset_component as assetHistoryComponent,ah.asset_component_modifier as assetHistoryComponentModifier,ah.last_modified_timestamp,max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Completed By' THEN value END) as "Completed By",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Transaction Date' THEN value END) as "Transaction Date",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Completed Date' THEN value END) as "Completed Date",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Work Order' THEN value END) as "Work Order",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Transaction Description' THEN value END) as "Transaction Description",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Schedule Date' THEN value END) as "Schedule Date",max(CASE WHEN aha.name = 'Work Group' THEN value END) as "Work Group"from asset_history ah join asset_history_attributes aha¾on ah.asset_history_id = aha.asset_history_idgroup by ah.asset_id, ah.asset_history_id, ah.type , ah.asset_component, ah.asset_component_modifier,ah.last_modified_timestamp order by last_modified_timestamp desc) tmpwhere asset_id =¾'<@asset_id_selected>' limit 5
ExpectedResponse: ID :1: equalTo(1),NAME:1: contains(Paul),AGE:1: equalTo(32),ADDRESS:1: isNotEmpty,                                        SALARY:1: equalTo(20000)
